13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 2357.302, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 2357.302. A. Except as provided in subsection F of
17 this section, for taxable years beginning after December 31, 2008,
18 and ending before January 1, 2026 tax years 2009 through 2031, a
19 qualified employer shall be allowed a credit against the tax imposed
20 pursuant to Section 2355 of this title for tuition reimbursed to a
21 qualified employee.
22 B. The credit authorized by subsection A of this section may be
23 claimed only if the qualified employee has been awarded an
24
