15 2. Five percent (5%) of the compensation paid for the first
16 through fifth years of employment in the aerospace sector if the
17 qualified employee graduated from an institution located outside
18 this state.
19 C. The credit authorized by this section shall not exceed
20 Twelve Thousand Five Hundred Dollars ($12,500.00) for each qualified
21 employee annually.
22 D. The credit authorized by this section shall not be used to
23 reduce the tax liability of the qualified employer to less than zero
24 (0).
